{"tid":356824,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想減肥請入","createTime":"2017-08-12T11:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-16T05:13:51.000Z","uid":35910,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f83a7f0b908cec492ffdd20b6e6deefcffd0ce5","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:47:12.000Z","msg":"如果你諗緊點減肥，可以睇睇。<br />\n之前我170cm高，90kg重，用左三個月甩左13kg，而家準備衝落70kg。<br />\n另外都想整合一啲迷思同資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1)飲食<br />\n走糖，我指走哂游離糖，少量果糖無礙，唔使全戒生果<br />\n游離糖即係砂糖同糖漿呢啲精製糖，嗰啲便利店茶餐廳凍飲，麵包蛋糕唔使諗。<br />\n<br />\n每日限制八小時飲食，正常減肥保持三餐即可，盡量清淡，大食者請減量。如想增肌就少食多餐，補充多啲蛋白質。<br />\n<br />\n謹記，每日最少補充800kcals。過少會影響新陳代謝，影響效果。七分飲食，三成運動！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2)運動<br />\n最佳減肥運動：游水，泰拳，西洋拳及MMA等拳擊運動，跑步(須留意扁平足同重量問題，重撚首選買Asics跑鞋)<br />\n<br />\n拳擊運動就簡單，多啲返去操有coach會推爆你氣同肌，一星期三日最基本，如覺得進步可增至一星期六日<br />\n<br />\n跑步同游水必須依自己能力調整強度，請盡量用中高強度的心率完成一段距離或時間，建議每星期兩至三日每次至少一小時中高強度運動，係辛苦啲，但為食係有代價的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3)適量增肌運動<br />\n除左去健身室之外，係屋企上Youtube有好多訓練可以做，增加肌肉係消脂好方法。<br />\n<br />\n稍後會Po幾個幾好既Exercise分享，即使細空間都可做，成效好過鄭多燕十萬倍。女仔唔好怕增肌，適量肌肉有線條美又可控制體重，益處甚多，呢啲又操唔到你爆肌的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4)恒心，信念<br />\n懶同怕辛苦既話，就收皮啦邊有不勞而獲，為食唔使代價？又想Fit又想型同靚，就要努力架啦。記住係為改變所以減肥，保持信念，恒心！唔好斷唔好停！"},{"pid":"510647421bb410e232b62cfa86ab26519143ccbd","tid":356824,"uid":134274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"LM支持 加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1e5f2b0583e26c75c14cd5a5f69987a4b5edd9","tid":356824,"uid":72506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"想知單車有無用？"},{"pid":"391ac7f16f217cb9c284970bcec695ebd3a062fd","tid":356824,"uid":131012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:01:40.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46b57d53f3b8f60303162d60e1e2c4ed778aadc","tid":356824,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:02:59.000Z","msg":"拳擊運動係咪好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"9055a66a7ca7d3b77fb69d4ecd3931c6a3a8d22c","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知單車有無用？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基本上所有帶氧運動都有用,最緊要Keep住強度!<br />\n<br />\nKeep住強度<br />\nKeep住強度<br />\nKeep住強度<br />\n<br />\n無強度,Hea完個時間或者距離嗰D諗都唔使諗!<br />\n<br />\n比較推薦要用全身既運動,外國有更多如美足,欖球<br />\n但我就列D香港本地易做既為主<br />\n全身運動一定更佳"},{"pid":"4821e1704bb9f39ea8144da760d556dd94556590","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拳擊運動係咪好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔貴呀~<br />\n有D館做包月都係2000樓下,一個月瘋狂上玩到你死<br />\n有D甚至1000蚊左右有十二堂<br />\n<br />\n如果有恆心同時間,首選包月,一定Fit<br />\n當然都要睇館,不過我就唔係度賣廣告了"},{"pid":"86817c649bcbdd766d1b6800aed98fb4f46a26b1","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LM支持 加油啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c57fff9c76027aa501026372e2ddc0f7a78f258","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見到好多人問，寫埋出黎啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0a82b6774ed85041544bed0949c06f3f6222bd","tid":356824,"uid":51730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:17:26.000Z","msg":"其實一開始可以只用飲食控制 <br />\n再計埋一日消耗同吸引既卡路里（熱量） 都會有效果 （有健身做重訓效果更佳）<br />\n<br />\n到停滯期再做下帶氧會好啲 唔好一開始減就做"},{"pid":"8ef929744a7fda675fcb2037930d5c1c792a337c","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實一開始可以只用飲食控制 <br />\n再計埋一日消耗同吸引既卡路里（熱量） 都會有效果 （有健身做重訓效果更佳）<br />\n<br />\n到停滯期再做下帶氧會好啲 唔好一開始減就做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果真係太肥，就散步減食為主，好快見效"},{"pid":"4c34167ad5d89075a5af7527bdc3f73899183439","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YdB1HMCldJY&amp;t=1386s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYdB1HMCldJY%26t%3D1386s&d=oRSwOeCmVPNmGg078MYj0pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=992e7b67\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YdB1HMCldJY&amp;t=1386s</a><br />\n呢個首選,清晰易明,一套做哂仲有熱身,每個Workday都唔同<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EIoryEvS2Gc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEIoryEvS2Gc&d=oRSwOeCmVPNmGg078MYj0pZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f7cdce0f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EIoryEvS2Gc</a><br />\n呢個練腹超級正<br />\n<br />\n我主力做呢兩個都已經見哂效"},{"pid":"27a41177c64386c6db44f3d7b936a3b79eb5c31d","tid":356824,"uid":42212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:23:07.000Z","msg":"路過留名學野"},{"pid":"8196171470daec370ccdbd2ac995244d305bacb6","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:33:18.000Z","msg":"5) 良好生活習慣<br />\n<br />\n唔煙唔酒呢D基本,請盡量早睡早起訓飽佢<br />\n訓覺係極重要環節,補充體力+肌肉生長+身體代謝能量消耗<br />\n盡量啦,都市人忙都無計<br />\n<br />\n飲水超級重要,請無時無刻都飲多D水,有好大幫助"},{"pid":"3062a8e2645b7e4a45029d07e4abc53eb4b1cd7e","tid":356824,"uid":92463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:34:36.000Z","msg":"lm。118kg 減到 101kg，繼續努力減緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4939b9b81ef0526b7829f7baab9ddfa375f87170","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T12:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lm。118kg 減到 101kg，繼續努力減緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08baa90a56216a7ac5e29d69fc2699f03c55ac70","tid":356824,"uid":81828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:17:40.000Z","msg":"淨係戒食肥野減左4kg而家停滯期<br />\n應該開始做有氧定無氧先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8be65f2474b4d7dba20449e9bc72f00d0003c45","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係戒食肥野減左4kg而家停滯期<br />\n應該開始做有氧定無氧先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戒左幾耐?有無戒糖?<br />\n一定要Keep住做有氧,睇下邊度出問題<br />\n每星期做幾多幾耐咩運動?<br />\n<br />\n幾高幾重?"},{"pid":"bfd15d5f75e28b094d8df9a54257a4429bd98249","tid":356824,"uid":50461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:28:12.000Z","msg":"瘦底但肥肚腩點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5cb7adef8f5776df7a77a2bd3ef654be546c5e","tid":356824,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"近190高 80kg, 點減?"},{"pid":"30317af13d753b74088c12080056e9f3269f5f52","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>瘦底但肥肚腩點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時生活習慣點,有無夜訓食煙飲酒,身體有無問題"},{"pid":"9faba001dd4c93da6026c14266c60a72d21e60a3","tid":356824,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:40:17.000Z","msg":"me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減咗三個幾月 64.5減到58 好慢<br />\n小目標係減到55 下年再減到50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1974ba7205c03c02e8f76f087bca82343edcc642","tid":356824,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"留名入黎減肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65571413c0d9f8c07c19c19be6b20dc54969b6e1","tid":356824,"uid":81828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>淨係戒食肥野減左4kg而家停滯期<br />\n應該開始做有氧定無氧先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戒左幾耐?有無戒糖?<br />\n一定要Keep住做有氧,睇下邊度出問題<br />\n每星期做幾多幾耐咩運動?<br />\n<br />\n幾高幾重?</blockquote><br />\n戒左一個月多啲 不嬲唔食甜冇特別戒<br />\n冇做任何運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住開始加運動 但唔知做有氧定無氧先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBmi 21-22"},{"pid":"49bd524cbb889a549fc89410a62b5ae6c1d10f8e","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>淨係戒食肥野減左4kg而家停滯期<br />\n應該開始做有氧定無氧先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戒左幾耐?有無戒糖?<br />\n一定要Keep住做有氧,睇下邊度出問題<br />\n每星期做幾多幾耐咩運動?<br />\n<br />\n幾高幾重?</blockquote><br />\n戒左一個月多啲 不嬲唔食甜冇特別戒<br />\n冇做任何運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住開始加運動 但唔知做有氧定無氧先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBmi 21-22</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先一個月啫,Run餐單同帶氧得啦<br />\n同埋BMI21-22睇落就OK既,肌肉量點?<br />\n睇下係咪要加D力量訓練?"},{"pid":"f9b386c53f882ff9bc73a46648e6a23363801c84","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近190高 80kg, 點減?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跟住我上面做左先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d3224a3f6aa5571df0003f98caf38135865579","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減咗三個幾月 64.5減到58 好慢<br />\n小目標係減到55 下年再減到50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藍絲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933992bdcd3f8a77a28baf5c4e6a0e2cb28f4dc6","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名入黎減肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMadao無架啦,廢柴大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7b9936b2c8d17e0ff2a6a6a06f6f278a6e51bf","tid":356824,"uid":81828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:55:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n戒左一個月多啲 不嬲唔食甜冇特別戒<br />\n冇做任何運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住開始加運動 但唔知做有氧定無氧先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBmi 21-22</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先一個月啫,Run餐單同帶氧得啦<br />\n同埋BMI21-22睇落就OK既,肌肉量點?<br />\n睇下係咪要加D力量訓練?</blockquote><br />\n好多贅肉 啲肉好鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪做你上面嗰兩段片就ok?"},{"pid":"ad1ca4b530474de62f40d8822ef566c962bfc294","tid":356824,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名入黎減肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMadao無架啦,廢柴大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我警告你千其唔好睇少大叔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"929f73dc669f3b0571b2195fb8388cc5bf0d624b","tid":356824,"uid":4057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T13:59:39.000Z","msg":"凍檸茶走甜應該ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大熱天時唔想飲熱野"},{"pid":"0b3692435d67434ca4317aae7c300e9a2c42f2ff","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n戒左一個月多啲 不嬲唔食甜冇特別戒<br />\n冇做任何運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住開始加運動 但唔知做有氧定無氧先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBmi 21-22</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先一個月啫,Run餐單同帶氧得啦<br />\n同埋BMI21-22睇落就OK既,肌肉量點?<br />\n睇下係咪要加D力量訓練?</blockquote><br />\n好多贅肉 啲肉好鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪做你上面嗰兩段片就ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYes,做上面兩段片已經好大幫助<br />\n片一有30days，有熱身有拉筋，超實用<br />\n片二主力練腹"},{"pid":"acdbbc4c7b74d3348017cee76f1980e3764cc34d","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:13:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>凍檸茶走甜應該ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大熱天時唔想飲熱野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家我都係叫凍檸水走甜，太熱了<br />\n凍檸水好Ｄ"},{"pid":"ed6bcd84ef04fe08ea34df7b0a79769c2b3b0f15","tid":356824,"uid":51730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>lm。118kg 減到 101kg，繼續努力減緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n65用左一個月減到53 用極端方法 低熱量+帶氧 重訓"},{"pid":"62da187d05d7436e38d56251f9ff1f47bae7b5c5","tid":356824,"uid":51730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減咗三個幾月 64.5減到58 好慢<br />\n小目標係減到55 下年再減到50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一個月65-&gt;53"},{"pid":"f596377a05a1593c913bf11b738123cbce672669","tid":356824,"uid":13904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n戒左一個月多啲 不嬲唔食甜冇特別戒<br />\n冇做任何運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住開始加運動 但唔知做有氧定無氧先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBmi 21-22</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先一個月啫,Run餐單同帶氧得啦<br />\n同埋BMI21-22睇落就OK既,肌肉量點?<br />\n睇下係咪要加D力量訓練?</blockquote><br />\n好多贅肉 啲肉好鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪做你上面嗰兩段片就ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYes,做上面兩段片已經好大幫助<br />\n片一有30days，有熱身有拉筋，超實用<br />\n片二主力練腹</blockquote><br />\n岩岩跟等一條片做左陣，但後面嗰啲唔係好做到 <br />\n第二條片更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a93c1077c561a0ecc8363e05d7bd2ab7686e8dd","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:54:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減咗三個幾月 64.5減到58 好慢<br />\n小目標係減到55 下年再減到50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一個月65-&gt;53</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係個個都得"},{"pid":"bcad7485f1cb3f516de6358ead3755fba0c9cd7d","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n戒左一個月多啲 不嬲唔食甜冇特別戒<br />\n冇做任何運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住開始加運動 但唔知做有氧定無氧先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBmi 21-22</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先一個月啫,Run餐單同帶氧得啦<br />\n同埋BMI21-22睇落就OK既,肌肉量點?<br />\n睇下係咪要加D力量訓練?</blockquote><br />\n好多贅肉 啲肉好鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪做你上面嗰兩段片就ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYes,做上面兩段片已經好大幫助<br />\n片一有30days，有熱身有拉筋，超實用<br />\n片二主力練腹</blockquote><br />\n岩岩跟等一條片做左陣，但後面嗰啲唔係好做到 <br />\n第二條片更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n萬事起頭難，堅持做落去<br />\n跟第一條片先，全面啲"},{"pid":"e69bdcfb7254655292f330d56e1c159e2af35924","tid":356824,"uid":13904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:08:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n戒左一個月多啲 不嬲唔食甜冇特別戒<br />\n冇做任何運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住開始加運動 但唔知做有氧定無氧先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBmi 21-22</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先一個月啫,Run餐單同帶氧得啦<br />\n同埋BMI21-22睇落就OK既,肌肉量點?<br />\n睇下係咪要加D力量訓練?</blockquote><br />\n好多贅肉 啲肉好鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪做你上面嗰兩段片就ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYes,做上面兩段片已經好大幫助<br />\n片一有30days，有熱身有拉筋，超實用<br />\n片二主力練腹</blockquote><br />\n岩岩跟等一條片做左陣，但後面嗰啲唔係好做到 <br />\n第二條片更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n萬事起頭難，堅持做落去<br />\n跟第一條片先，全面啲</blockquote><br />\n一個肥仔點做引體上升 掌上壓都係做到10下<br />\n應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f108e28d7e0bd4d2657a10a1e66b554fc80fa758","tid":356824,"uid":9436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 減咗三個幾月 64.5減到58 好慢<br />\n小目標係減到55 下年再減到50<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一個月65-&gt;53</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係個個都得</blockquote><br />\n我斬咗隻腳就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d316a9547dcdd2bc96be267606ff0237c7c7988c","tid":356824,"uid":50461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>瘦底但肥肚腩點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時生活習慣點,有無夜訓食煙飲酒,身體有無問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔煙少酒 唔算夜訓 不過成日都口痕 出去食野成日感覺多左 唔知係咪關事 身體無乜問題 定我去check下好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b361ef2ad4dab2df57d0f22a74c225020bfcc5d","tid":356824,"uid":81828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T20:20:59.000Z","msg":"冇時間運動 Youtube嗰啲4-15分鐘嘅HIIT可唔可以代替跑步之類嘅有氧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24f191555b523fd4f201f5f56f2e9bca25ccdb5","tid":356824,"uid":54744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T21:09:20.000Z","msg":"經過比d劣見，如果係減<br />\n全身既帶氧運動加肌肉訓練係維持得最好<br />\n自己減得最快瘦得最明顯果排<br />\n係keep住長跑但極小操肌肉，仲有瘋狂忍口<br />\n之後覺醒佐我流失大量肌肉，唔可以再鳩減<br />\n由90幾kg肥仔用佐3年時間慢慢改善生活習慣<br />\n例如唔食太多白飯，改食多d餸，soft drink盡量減小，keep住一個頻率做唔同exercise同帶氧<br />\n到依加70 kg, 肚腩仔同大屎忽雖然都仲有d<br />\n但身型上已經比起90 kg好得好多<br />\n由加大碼著到s/m size<br />\n依加食乜都得，甚至傷佐一排都冇反彈過<br />\n依加努力做腹同埋屎忽大脾既work out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都好睇你想要咩成果，如果係急住要成果同埋想要比較靚既身型，我既經歷就唔啱洗，直情係垃圾<br />\n不過如果只係想生活開心，可以著到多d衫又食野唔洗怕肥，我覺得我自己依加係一個幾好既例子，畢竟我用佐3年，廢就認既，但減肥已經係我生活既一部份"},{"pid":"99e1b7f31a7b889e381e16fd13cd48458798be54","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n戒左一個月多啲 不嬲唔食甜冇特別戒<br />\n冇做任何運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住開始加運動 但唔知做有氧定無氧先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBmi 21-22</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先一個月啫,Run餐單同帶氧得啦<br />\n同埋BMI21-22睇落就OK既,肌肉量點?<br />\n睇下係咪要加D力量訓練?</blockquote><br />\n好多贅肉 啲肉好鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪做你上面嗰兩段片就ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nYes,做上面兩段片已經好大幫助<br />\n片一有30days，有熱身有拉筋，超實用<br />\n片二主力練腹</blockquote><br />\n岩岩跟等一條片做左陣，但後面嗰啲唔係好做到 <br />\n第二條片更加唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n萬事起頭難，堅持做落去<br />\n跟第一條片先，全面啲</blockquote><br />\n一個肥仔點做引體上升 掌上壓都係做到10下<br />\n應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n引體不要急，我第二條片個Channel有教引體要訣，肥人唔係咁易<br />\n先做第一條片訓練全身肌肉，持之以恒"},{"pid":"f9b4b40f09bcc325006af83934faa2564e5b6d66","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>瘦底但肥肚腩點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平時生活習慣點,有無夜訓食煙飲酒,身體有無問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔煙少酒 唔算夜訓 不過成日都口痕 出去食野成日感覺多左 唔知係咪關事 身體無乜問題 定我去check下好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n口痕食零食同出街食肥膩野？<br />\n有無運動？"},{"pid":"091b42b0124042a2a79387261e912405ba84aed4","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:17:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇時間運動 Youtube嗰啲4-15分鐘嘅HIIT可唔可以代替跑步之類嘅有氧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不能！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfcb2699e0f5f7a19f1652108f510cc4365fbcb","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>經過比d劣見，如果係減<br />\n全身既帶氧運動加肌肉訓練係維持得最好<br />\n自己減得最快瘦得最明顯果排<br />\n係keep住長跑但極小操肌肉，仲有瘋狂忍口<br />\n之後覺醒佐我流失大量肌肉，唔可以再鳩減<br />\n由90幾kg肥仔用佐3年時間慢慢改善生活習慣<br />\n例如唔食太多白飯，改食多d餸，soft drink盡量減小，keep住一個頻率做唔同exercise同帶氧<br />\n到依加70 kg, 肚腩仔同大屎忽雖然都仲有d<br />\n但身型上已經比起90 kg好得好多<br />\n由加大碼著到s/m size<br />\n依加食乜都得，甚至傷佐一排都冇反彈過<br />\n依加努力做腹同埋屎忽大脾既work out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都好睇你想要咩成果，如果係急住要成果同埋想要比較靚既身型，我既經歷就唔啱洗，直情係垃圾<br />\n不過如果只係想生活開心，可以著到多d衫又食野唔洗怕肥，我覺得我自己依加係一個幾好既例子，畢竟我用佐3年，廢就認既，但減肥已經係我生活既一部份</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n觀念幾好，落到去要Keep住，良好既生活同運動習慣依然重要，加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時欲速則不達"},{"pid":"9d83a3c3accb40a704d0e238c546429b2eef7fdd","tid":356824,"uid":54411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/092316_560138d1f9a04ae5bc78915c5d43ed3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F092316_560138d1f9a04ae5bc78915c5d43ed3f.jpg&h=f65c3917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n識做一定做 無氧增肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（有氧運動過程中 有可能消耗左 珍貴的肌肉）"},{"pid":"beb62f4c463593c6d9e5a3dfac8ab51d7df80a24","tid":356824,"uid":35910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T01:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/092316_560138d1f9a04ae5bc78915c5d43ed3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F092316_560138d1f9a04ae5bc78915c5d43ed3f.jpg&h=f65c3917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n識做一定做 無氧增肌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（有氧運動過程中 有可能消耗左 珍貴的肌肉）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n減重絕對要帶氧消脂同重量訓練<br />\n<br />\n到合適重量先做多啲無氧專門增肌"},{"pid":"dba7e32a3127da78a718eed4add0feac116e0ca7","tid":356824,"uid":85431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T02:08:27.000Z","msg":"減唔到"}]}